The paper discusses a conversational paradigm for product search, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories. However, since the focus is on product search and feedback, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category.
